# S03 — FRONTEND_DEV Brief: eWeLink Refinement

role: FRONTEND_DEV
sprint: S03
stack: Vue 3, Vite, Tailwind, Socket.IO-client, Chart.js

tasks:
  - Dashboard section for eWeLink devices (glassmorphism, responsive)
  - DeviceCard component: status, channels, on/off toggle
  - Chart component for power consumption (if API provides data)
  - Socket.IO listener for live device updates

implementation:
  - Use `<script setup>`, ref/reactive, computed for chart data
  - Tailwind utility-first; dark mode support
  - Micro-animations for status transitions
  - No hardcoded API URLs (use proxy/.env)

reusability:
  - Card and chart designed for Tuya devices in S04
  - Props: device-type, channels, status; slots for custom controls

anti-patterns:
  - Heavy logic in templates
  - Large monolithic components (split by concern)
